description: |
  The Hurd Property, Bates Land, and Blackman Land form one trail network. Parking is 
  available off of Old Ayer Road, Skyfields Drive, and at Indian Hill Road. The
  Skyfields Drive trail climbs the Indian Hills, passes the former 
  <a href="http://www.nelsap.org/ma/skyfields.html">Skyfields Ski Area</a>, 
  with the the summit providing open vistas of western Massachusetts, and 
  an orchard on Bates Lands. This trail is highly recommended.  
  
